{"tid":2500167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對香港滿滿的愛：日本人製作《機動武鬥傳G高達》主題香港旅遊書","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T15:52:54.000Z","uid":261647,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7979a0bf3cb477f106c462713fe375674357ba","tid":2500167,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/anime/g-gundam-in-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fanime%2Fg-gundam-in-hk%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=9bf4ff98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/anime/g-gundam-in-hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcG7fTqJADY9GRDvaoP2rspSDyKz9KByerDoFoW8WVyj2?filename=EsZu6Kn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsZu6Kn.png&h=4f75a4e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/日本有心人-製作《機動武鬥傳G高達》同人香港旅遊書-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA-%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E6%A9%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%AD%A6%E9%AC%A5%E5%82%B3G%E9%AB%98%E9%81%94%E3%80%8B%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%9B%B8-1024x576.jpg&h=0d006209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《機動武鬥傳G高達》可謂是日本動畫對昔日香港致敬的佼佼者。最近就有位《機動武鬥傳G高達》的日本人粉絲おとなしじゃっく出版了一本結合該作元素的旅遊書，為日本人介紹香港，令人深深感受到其對香港文化的熱愛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/G高達-同人香港旅遊書-真品.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FG%E9%AB%98%E9%81%94-%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%9B%B8-%E7%9C%9F%E5%93%81.jpg&h=d99ae978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶着對作品滿滿熱愛的香港旅遊書<br />\n<br />\n書中第一頁就是香港地圖，不僅標明香港主要地方，亦有註上《機動武鬥傳G高達》主要情節發生的地點，方便粉絲聖地巡禮！作者不僅自己繪製有關乘搭香港航空飛抵香港的搞笑Q版漫畫，更收錄了故事主角們在香港遊歷的同人插圖，完全感受到發行人想要對作品以及香港文化致敬的熱情！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Unknown-5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FUnknown-5.jpeg&h=7f0a30a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主角於文武廟遊樂場面<br />\n<br />\n這真是一本真的旅遊指南<br />\n<br />\n作為一本旅遊指南，發行人おとなしじゃっく非常詳細地記下了在香港旅行的注意事項和香港特色。由航空公司，酒店予約乃至香港美食和旅行預算等等，一應俱全均有介紹。此外，作者會為較熱門的旅遊景點如女人街等特別說明，並附上個人感想。書中更記載了三日兩夜以及一日遊的推薦行程，方便不同類型想來香港旅行的日本人。實在想不到日本竟會有人對香港有如此深入的瞭解！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Unknown-3-2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FUnknown-3-2.jpeg&h=7aa7a63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n書中介紹了香港樂去處<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Unknown.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FUnknown.jpeg&h=6fb2f6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連旅行必備物品都有介紹，對國外旅行的新手也照顧周到<br />\n<br />\n在日本也可以感受香港文化<br />\n<br />\n礙於肺炎病毒肆虐，香港人暫時未能到日本旅行玩樂，對於日本人來說亦是如此。故書中特別介紹了在日本可以享用香港美食的餐廳，令人可於疫情下一解對香港美食的渴求，感受香港文化！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Unknown-4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FUnknown-4.jpeg&h=687124e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港飲食文化不得不提的「飲茶」，日本也有「茶樓」<br />\n<br />\n特稿！與香港粉絲對話<br />\n<br />\n本書後段設有特稿，訪問了《機動武鬥傳G高達》的香港粉絲對作品的看法。訪談不僅講述了香港粉絲對G高達的感受，亦記載了香港人對日本人粉絲的信息。一部90年代的經典動畫至今依然連結港日兩地，實在非常溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Unknown-2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FUnknown-2.jpeg&h=1b6b5d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n書末更附有發行人來港時的「蝦碌」奇遇，非常搞笑，對這本高質素香港旅遊書有興趣的人可到以下連結參閱更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n作品購買網站：<a href=\"https://jackotonashi.booth.pm/items/2780321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackotonashi.booth.pm%2Fitems%2F2780321&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=dc44e24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jackotonashi.booth.pm/items/2780321</a><br />\n發行人 おとなしじゃっくTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jackotonashi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjackotonashi&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=28e14165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jackotonashi</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/likejpn/posts/3672861249490423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flikejpn%2Fposts%2F3672861249490423&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=df8d59bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/likejpn/posts/3672861249490423</a><br />\n<br />\n宮澤茉莉:<br />\nおとなしじゃっくです。<br />\n我最鍾意嘅香港，我最鍾意嘅G高達，我畫咗一本書。<br />\n感謝您撰寫文章！ 我期待住有一日再次訪問香港得！"},{"pid":"d71c0125d82d28ae2c0f8cc1cea996f264ec96f4","tid":2500167,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4a5f053bef2013e7f8e5dfca4e207d6db6ce7e","tid":2500167,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89b8c495339baebc1ccaa2ff056bf10926c4f15","tid":2500167,"uid":137732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3600cbd4e6a05fef717eda67f972e7f44ecd7384","tid":2500167,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"又迫我睇多次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf92c